title: Mood Snap, AI That Reads Your Pet’s Mood
description: WoafMeow Mood Snap 📸😸 – AI That Reads Your Pet’s Mood Instantly! Snap or upload a pic, and our AI analyzes expressions, posture, and micro-expressions to reveal your pet’s mood. Excited, curious, relaxed, or plotting world domination (cats, we see you 😼).
